If you are a 1st Gen holder or you have more than 1 EtherHeads in your wallet please keep on eye on further announcements as we have something extra for you. We are keeping priority to provide real value and exclusive access to our holders.

The reasoning behind this is that we would like to stay away from Whitelist grinding in our Discord and in general, and focus on building a strong community. Zsolt wants to introduce this with the 4 abstract collection releases in April.
